 after paying attention to the traditional rules of grammar and basic construction. Just inverting sentences or haphazardly decapitalizing words to try to immitate or create poetic style without understanding what it is one is doing is bad. However, you seem to be sound in mind and know what you are doing. Poetic style is poetic style. Do what you want to achieve effect.<br>
